install sonarqube 
install sonarscanner
install sonarqube scanner
Goto jenkins --> manage jenkins --> configure and give sonarqube server url and port no
and create token in sonarqube and add that token here in configuraion

Goto jenkins  --> manage jenkins   -->global tool configuraion
here add sonarqube scanner  
sonar name - sonar_scanner
sonar path - /opt/sonar_scanner

apply and save

create a job in that conf --> build --> execute sonarqube scanner
give analysis properties
sonar.projectKey=Valaxy
sonar.projectName=ValaxyDemo
sonar.projectVersion=1.0
sonar.sources=/var/lib/jenkins/workspace/$JOB_NAME/<PROJECT_NAME>/src

and run . than you can see in sonarqube
